name: White Papaya
description: White Papaya is a hybrid weed strain made from a genetic cross between The White and Papaya. Bred by Oni Seed Company, White Papaya is 26% THC, making this strain an ideal choice for experienced cannabis consumers. Leafly customers tell us White Papaya effects make them feel focused, uplifted, and aroused. Medical marijuana patients often choose White Papaya when dealing with symptoms associated with depression, fatigue, and cramps. The dominant terpene of this cannabis strain is limonene. White Papaya features an aroma and flavor profile of nutty honey and mango.
